2. Invalid JWT signature â†’ 401 Unauthorized + redirect to /mock-login
3. User not found in mock config â†’ 401 Unauthorized + redirect to /mock-login
4. Insufficient permissions â†’ 403 Forbidden
5. Resource not found â†’ 404 Not Found
